text: The Key () is a 1983 Italian erotic drama movie directed by Tinto Brass and was based on the 1956 novel of the same name by Junichiro Tanizaki. It stars Frank Finlay, Stefania Sandrelli, Barbara Cupisti, Ricky Tognazzi, Ugo Tognazzi. ==Other websites== * Category:1983 drama movies Category:1980s erotic movies Category:Italian drama movies Category:Movies based on books Category:Movies directed by Tinto Brass Category:Movies set in the 1940s Category:Movies about sexual repression Category:Movies set in Venice
